s, debug artifacts, or missing files\n4. If anything fails: one retry via Gemini, then do it yourself\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7fe66ef0-d5d2-4812-aac6-1e203713ae0a","uuid":"79574f2f-12ff-4f43-affc-a45561cfdacd","isSynthetic":true}
